50|$|CALIPSO {{has also}} been used in {{conjunction}} with the MODIS data to determine how aerosols within the planetary boundary layer might alter low planetary boundary layer stratus clouds. The detection of biomass burning aerosols were shown to decrease the cloud droplet radius within these warm <b>layer</b> <b>clouds</b> in agreement with the Albrecht effect, while simultaneously decreasing liquid water path in contrast to the Albrecht effect.|$|E
